this lifetime.

00:23:22.920 --> 00:23:26.430 align:middle line:84%
That's what carries forward
from one life to the other,

00:23:26.430 --> 00:23:27.345 align:middle line:90%
in my view.

00:23:27.345 --> 00:23:29.220 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Absolutely,
